✅ What is Jackson? (in short)
Jackson is a Java library used by Spring Boot to convert JSON ↔ Java objects automatically.

🔁 What Jackson does
JSON → Java Object (Deserialization)
Java Object → JSON (Serialization)

📌 Example
{ "name": "Rahul", "age": 21 }
⬇

Student student;
Jackson does this conversion automatically when you use:

@RequestBody
@ResponseBody
@RestController